{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "托我买的东西都买好了。\\n稍微逛一会儿怎么样，霍克？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "不，\\n我不太喜欢吵闹……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "真冷淡啊。\\n稍微给点面子嘛。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "唉……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "席尔瓦？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "女子",
            "context": "你是……席尔瓦吧？\\n啊……没想到会在这里遇到你！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "女子",
            "context": "我一直……一直在找你……\\n你到底跑哪里去了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "不，不是……我叫……霍克。\\n我不认识什么席尔瓦……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "你、你认错人……了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "喂喂，霍克！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "女子",
            "context": "怎么会……席尔瓦……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "喂，霍克，你怎么这么紧张？\\n不像你平时那么冷静。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "兰扎卜，\\n能不能帮我一个忙？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "帮忙？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "女子",
            "context": "诶……这、这里是？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "没错。你找的那个\\n叫席尔瓦的男人，长眠在这里。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "他在路上突然倒下的时候，\\n我救了他，但他太虚弱，\\n很快便死了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "女子",
            "context": "怎、怎么会……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "抱歉，因为我只知道名字，\\n所以没法告诉你关于他的事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "女子",
            "context": "呜、呜呜……席尔瓦……\\n呜呜呜呜呜……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "那样真的好吗？真是的，\\n让我演个对不起人家的角色……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "抱歉……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "然后呢？\\n你会告诉我事情原委吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "好吧……接下来要讲的故事……\\n是关于一个消失了的男人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "名叫席尔瓦的男人有三位青梅竹马。\\n活泼的加里，聪明的马鲁库斯\\n和心地善良的碧蕾尔。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "席尔瓦、加里和马鲁库斯\\n都喜欢碧蕾尔。\\n所以三人私底下约定……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "长大后要成为\\n能让碧蕾尔幸福的出色人物。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "时光流逝……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "加里成了骑士，马鲁库斯成了祭司，\\n而席尔瓦……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "当时，\\n成了人们口中的“狩人者”……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "但席尔瓦不后悔。\\n虽然身为杀手的自己\\n无法再去见碧蕾尔……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "但他认为另外两人\\n可以代替沾满鲜血的自己，\\n给她幸福。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "就在那时，两份暗杀任务\\n送到了席尔瓦手里。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "一份要求暗杀加里，\\n另一份要求暗杀马鲁库斯……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "被称为“狩人者”的席尔瓦\\n无法对自己童年的伙伴下手。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "席尔瓦向两人\\n坦白了一切。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "坦白自己是“狩人者”，\\n坦白有人要杀了他们二人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "但这反而招致了恶果。\\n因为……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "暗杀的委托人\\n正是加里和马鲁库斯。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "两人出人头地、获得权力后成为政敌，\\n都觉得对方碍眼。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "所以便委托了本领高强的杀手，\\n殊不知杀手正是席尔瓦……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "席尔瓦知道真相时\\n为时已晚，\\n加里和马鲁库斯都已被杀……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "加里和马鲁库斯\\n得知席尔瓦没有接受委托，\\n便委托了其他杀手。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "于是，同时失去两个童年玩伴的\\n席尔瓦逃离了故乡……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "席尔瓦这个名字已经舍弃在故乡。\\n站在这里的，是连栖身之树\\n都没有的可怜的鹰。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "原来发生过这种事……\\n那刚才的女子就是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "是碧蕾尔。虽然这是我们长大后\\n第一次见面，但她竟然还能认出我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "真的好吗？\\n那种离别方式……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "事到如今，已无可奈何。\\n是我夺走了她的幸福。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "霍克……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "我至今还会想，那个时候……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "如果我选择杀死加里或马鲁库斯\\n其中一个，另一个就不用死了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "那样的话，至少碧蕾尔还能得到幸福。\\n然而……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "直到现在，\\n我都不知道该怎么办……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110267_01_03_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}